(1, 2, 'What is Growing Up?', 'text', NULL, 'Growing up means your body and mind slowly change as you get older. Everyone grows at their own pace, and that is normal.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 10, 1, '2026-02-14 20:47:39', '2026-02-16 21:03:47');

